          "reviewBody": "i was a student of this school and tbh this school is not for learning but you can get demotivated here easily the teachers of this school not only demotivates but also tell us that we wont achieve  anything in our life just because we didnt complete our notebook..the principal of this school  had 0 knowledge of art and said to my brother that from this type of art he we wont do anything in his career but guess what he is now studying in one of the best design universities in india.",
