            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I was student of this school for only 7 Months. My First Day of this school I was scolded by a teacher, even the students had troubled me a lot. Many times students used to false accusation on me, So many times I used to be punished even when it is not my mistake. Once I was taken to Principal Mam by pulling my hand in front of full class. Even many times teachers had shouted on my mother, many times she had cried in front of them. Never a day missed when a teacher did not scold me or insulted me. So forcefully, I had to leave the school. I was new in that school and even in the Area. However, we got good response nor in the School nor in the Area. Therefore, I Left the school and the Area.",
